        dc:description           "FIGURES 39–46. Pyropteron Biology. 39. Armeria canescens, hostplant of Pyropteron hellenicum, Greece, Epirus, Timfi Mts, Gamila. 40–41. Pyropteron borreyi, (40) female, Morocco, High Atlas, Oukaimeden, (41) male, Morocco, Middle Alas, Col du Zad. 42–43. Pyropteron maroccana, males, Morocco, High Atlas, Oukaimeden (images FP). 44. Pyropteron hispanica, female, reared, Spain, Toledo, Buenasbodas. 45–46. Pyropteron koschwitzi, (45) male, reared, Spain, Aranjuez, (46) female, reared, Spain, Castile, Navacepedilla (images Zdeněk Laštůvka)." ;
